<i>adverb</i>: 꾸물꾸물 [꾸물꾸물], 곰지락곰지락 [곰지락꼼지락] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>꾸물꾸물 [꾸물꾸물]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with slow moves</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 매우 느리게 자꾸 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of something moving repeatedly and very slowly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sluggishly; tardily</dd><br>
<dd>느리고 게으르게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of behaving slowly and lazily.</dd><br>
<dd>3. with slow moves</dd><br>
<dd>신체 일부를 자꾸 느리게 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of moving some parts of the body repeatedly and slowly.</dd><br>
<dt>곰지락곰지락 [곰지락꼼지락]</dt><br>
<dd>sluggishly; tardily</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 천천히 조금씩 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving the body slowly and little by little.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>